021import net.tnemc.item.AbstractItemStack;
022
023import java.util.Map;
024
025/**
026 * BundleComponent - The items stored inside this bundle.
027 *
028 * @see <a href="https://minecraft.wiki/w/Data_component_format#bundle_contents">Reference</a>
029 * @author creatorfromhell
030 * @since 0.2.0.0
031 */
032public abstract class BundleComponent<I extends AbstractItemStack<T>, T> extends ContainerComponent<I, T> {
033
034  public BundleComponent() {
035    super();
036  }
037
038  public BundleComponent(final Map<Integer, AbstractItemStack<T>> items) {
039
040    super(items);
041  }
042
043  @Override
044  public String identifier() {
045    return "bundle";
046  }
047}
